{"tid":1368184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發奇腸] 獨立調查委員會 可能唔係最好既方法","createTime":"2019-07-26T12:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T15:01:52.000Z","uid":220942,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1e22f5b87c43d173fd06baa8bebb42371ec97fb5","tid":1368184,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:17:54.000Z","msg":"最近多左post 講ICAC 當初成立原因<br />\n簡單就係警察貪污, 政府要成立ICAC去打貪, 而打貪對象主要係一班警察<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BB%89%E6%94%BF%E5%85%AC%E7%BD%B2_(%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25BB%2589%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%25BD%25B2_%28%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%29&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07rtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=32665ba2\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BB%89%E6%94%BF%E5%85%AC%E7%BD%B2_(%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF)</a><br />\n<br />\nwiki寫道<br />\n<em>六七暴動後，香港總督戴麟趾意識到貪污問題的嚴重性，以及原有《防止貪污條例》的不足，於是在1971年5月制定《防止賄賂條例》，以加重針對貪污的罰則、擴大懲治範圍、以及賦予反貪污部更大的權力去偵查貪污案件[11]。然而，儘管英國朝野日益關注香港的貪污情況，戴麟趾任內肅貪的力度始終有限度，他接受英國電視台訪問談及貪污問題時，更被批評為「像一根圖騰柱僵硬地坐在攝影機前，言語唐突，態度曖昧」[12]。</em><br />\n<br />\n<em>1973年8月26日，大批學生和市民在銅鑼灣維多利亞公園舉行「反貪污，捉葛柏」集會，但是警察事後卻票控部份參與集會的人士，繼而引發不少香港市民在9月16日再舉行「貪污有罪，集會無罪」的示威，聲援被檢控的集會人士，種種事件反映出公眾對港英政府打擊貪污不力的不滿[14]。</em><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係咪同而家發生緊既事好似樣呢</span><br />\n<br />\n講番而家既問題, <br />\n係警察同黑社會勾結, 警黑合作公然傷害香港市民, 而家唔係單獨幾個黑警, 而係高高低低各層既警察都一樣同流合污<br />\n<br />\n如果, 就算成立獨立調查委員會, 都只係可以解決到今次既紛爭。長遠黎講警察將來仍有好大可能會繼續警黑合作,警黑合作將以更高層次進行。<br />\n<br />\n所以, 我地應該<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要求政府成立一個獨立部門</span></span> , 架構同ICAC一樣, under 香港首長 , 獨立及直接向香港政府首長。獨立部門將會負責調查警隊職權及職能上不合法或不負責既投訴。<br />\n<br />\n係 獨立調查委員會 同 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">獨立部門</span></span> 兩者之間, 我地應該選擇一個獨立部門以解長遠之憂"},{"pid":"364973c626235d66601b5204da4f70788fbb6139","tid":1368184,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:20:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f815bf3fb701c9613ff808c2691ea73d34a116fa","tid":1368184,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:29:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"beb8d992063a8794cf8a711df05ed86c9ef53e3a","tid":1368184,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:39:50.000Z","msg":"不要說「五大訴求」，試著說「警黑合作」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1367891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1367891</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"75a7733aa81b0dadbc43c70035428f4850d0ed38","tid":1368184,"uid":196430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:41:25.000Z","msg":"既然警犬開始醞釀政變，我哋係時候提高offer<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dqArnS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dqArnS</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71b9853e98fb6c6256481838ca64e37b7d5972b","tid":1368184,"uid":81424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:42:22.000Z","msg":"要雙普選先<br />\n乜都假"},{"pid":"d1b1755e54e336fbde9e0e1b07a3b67cc52466c2","tid":1368184,"uid":220942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75a7733aa81b0dadbc43c70035428f4850d0ed38","tid":1368184,"uid":196430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:41:25.000Z","msg":"既然警犬開始醞釀政變，我哋係時候提高offer<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dqArnS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dqArnS</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係黑警知道自己犯法都唔會有咩後果, 佢地先咁L黑警<br />\n要俾佢地知有後果,佢地就唔敢"},{"pid":"0b87a379cb0d34d421fdbe2d5eb59db68bd0245c","tid":1368184,"uid":263174,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:53:19.000Z","msg":"under行政長官有L用咩，而家係成個行政機關加立法機關被西環控制，立一個行政或立法機關去制衡己經無用。獨立調查委員會都係靠法官加持，先有少少可信力。真普選或獨立係唯一一途。再唔係就普選一個有搜証權力的監警會。"},{"pid":"b25cac1237fe109ab3ee9828d85a5b71d6ee1caa","tid":1368184,"uid":103013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:56:05.000Z","msg":"你訓醒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a67f3c305a80cfbdbcfa4dfcdfd8bb8588272d","tid":1368184,"uid":245441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b25cac1237fe109ab3ee9828d85a5b71d6ee1caa","tid":1368184,"uid":103013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:56:05.000Z","msg":"你訓醒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:07:19.000Z","msg":"成立中紀委？"},{"pid":"9a00081494870d53eb8c3b3967cbde851d3e0256","tid":1368184,"uid":220942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0b87a379cb0d34d421fdbe2d5eb59db68bd0245c","tid":1368184,"uid":263174,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:53:19.000Z","msg":"under行政長官有L用咩，而家係成個行政機關加立法機關被西環控制，立一個行政或立法機關去制衡己經無用。獨立調查委員會都係靠法官加持，先有少少可信力。真普選或獨立係唯一一途。再唔係就普選一個有搜証權力的監警會。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:18:15.000Z","msg":"under行政長官係因為冇其他方法, 政府架構一定要report俾上面果個<br />\nICAC 仲有少少用, 都係照炒ICAC 啫<br />\n<br />\n況且係入面做既, 多數都係香港人"},{"pid":"fbecf566659cb6572375eaaa79e458d2f80a3424","tid":1368184,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b25cac1237fe109ab3ee9828d85a5b71d6ee1caa","tid":1368184,"uid":103013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:56:05.000Z","msg":"你訓醒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:19:22.000Z","msg":"如果你係黑警 , 你驚獨立調查委員會多啲, 定驚ICAC / 獨立部門多啲?"},{"pid":"9a3b684a758e5613bb990f2f04765461912a9cce","tid":1368184,"uid":190521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:14:50.000Z","msg":"先推一推"},{"pid":"a52aff67e8aee9ff8d1002f853b94cf8a60ec00a","tid":1368184,"uid":75412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:15:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>個幾月黎, 多謝咁多位勇武, 聽日靠你地保護老少婦孺, 希望唔好主動出手, 但唔代表唔還手<br />\n<br />\n和理非帶埋後備電, 盡量全程錄影, 有咩事可以還原真相<br />\n<br />\n記住, 我們要嘅係呢次運動嘅勝利, 唔係贏一場交<br />\n<br />\n勇武 和理非 永不分割<br />\n</strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"e235d4a999133c5e58f0eb2292ff68459a583690","tid":1368184,"uid":190521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:15:34.000Z","msg":"其實獨立調查<br />\n隨時不了了之<br />\n分分鐘拖成年都冇人care<br />\n求其搵人祭旗就算"},{"pid":"88182548c89ce0c90421a8282baf50644133412e","tid":1368184,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:17:16.000Z","msg":"成立都冇用 要告先得"},{"pid":"6ee5fd668a3dd8c8062d07bb1958336df4f3fb75","tid":1368184,"uid":220942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"88182548c89ce0c90421a8282baf50644133412e","tid":1368184,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:17:16.000Z","msg":"成立都冇用 要告先得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:51:55.000Z","msg":"我個諗法係 高度獨立部門 ，就似icac咁，絕對有調查權力，同埋可以刑事提告。<br />\n<br />\n政府而家冇一個部門可以獨立查警察，咁咪成立一個，如果話淨係查警察太針對，咁可以將負責範圍放大到唔止警察，對象係包埋其他政府人員，或者市民。<br />\n<br />\nicac都係警察貪污冇人治到佢地，而特登成立。<br />\n咁同黑社會勾結呢方便都同樣可以做。<br />\n<br />\n如果話under特首做唔到野，咁我相信個部門入面工作既香港都順便監察埋個機構。"},{"pid":"968912db42be5a6a9e0126f67afe6ca432a37466","tid":1368184,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e235d4a999133c5e58f0eb2292ff68459a583690","tid":1368184,"uid":190521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:15:34.000Z","msg":"其實獨立調查<br />\n隨時不了了之<br />\n分分鐘拖成年都冇人care<br />\n求其搵人祭旗就算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:57:12.000Z","msg":"exact7ly, 就係咁。<br />\n<br />\n如果我係藍衫或者低級白衫，就會好L驚獨立部門<br />\n驚起想黎，寧願都係要獨立調查算。<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有獨立部門，藍衫一定會係首先私下告密果班"},{"pid":"825bb753aeeb975db10dc835a3624e9d0673f472","tid":1368184,"uid":190521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:01:52.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"}]}